  "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/TrustTunnel/TrustTunnelClient/tarball/v1.0.49",
  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/TrustTunnel/TrustTunnelClient/zipball/v1.0.49",
  "body": "This release improves **security of DNS handling** and extends **deep-link capabilities** for more complete client configuration.\r\n\r\nPlease see corresponding releases with improved deep-link support:\r\n- TrustTunnel endpoint: https://github.com/TrustTunnel/TrustTunnel/releases/tag/v1.0.33\r\n- TrustTunnel Flutter client: https://github.com/TrustTunnel/TrustTunnelFlutterClient/releases/tag/v1.1.1.6401-release\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 🎯 Highlights\r\n- Enhanced **deep-link support** #58 \r\n  - Import DNS upstreams and server name directly from deep-link  \r\n  - `dns_upstreams` moved to `[endpoint]` section (backward compatible)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 🔒 Security\r\n- Secured the service socket used for DNS query forwarding to prevent misuse by processes running localhost port scans #62\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 🔧 Notes\r\n- Legacy `dns_upstreams` in the root config is still supported for compatibility with older configs",
